### API Information
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/health

### Get All Hotels
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/hotels

### Get Hotel by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/hotels/{{hotelId}}

### Create Hotel
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/hotels
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Grand Luxury Hotel",
  "description": "A premium 5-star hotel in the heart of the city",
  "address": "123 Main Street",
  "city": "New York",
  "country": "USA",
  "phone": "+1234567890",
  "email": "info@grandluxury.com",
  "rating": 5,
  "isActive": true
}

### Update Hotel
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/v1/hotels/{{hotelId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Grand Luxury Hotel & Spa",
  "rating": 5,
  "description": "Updated description"
}

### Delete Hotel (Soft Delete)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/v1/hotels/{{hotelId}}
